Author: Marcostar02
Text: Self harm is a very hard road to travel. Itâ€™s rough in the fact that there are so many things that can be self harm. Glad to see that you saw the signs and pulled yourself back from it before you let yourself get any deeper.

Author: ChristieFox
Text: I also feel bingeing can be a form of self harm. I saw that when I didn't even lost control while bingeing, I just ate to feel bad after it.  It's so hard to stop because most other forms of coping mechanisms for me are also self harm. Probably learning to cope healthily should be the first step.
